data.description: FHA Assumable Loan on this tranquil charm of Lockwood, Montana, in this spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom split-entry home. As you walk in, the open floor plan immediately welcomes you, leading into an ample-sized kitchen that meets all your culinary needs with plenty of storage. four well-sized bedrooms—offering plenty of space for family or guests. Beyond the interior, the property boasts a generous lot size, perfect for gardening, raising animals, or simply enjoying the great outdoors. Step out onto the expansive two-level deck overlooking your private yard for entertainment or relaxation. Vehicle and storage needs are easily met with a detached 2-car garage and additional parking spaces for RVs, extra vehicles, and outdoor "toys." Don't miss this unique opportunity to own a piece of Montana paradise.  $5000 credit for buyers choice of rate buy down,  closing costs,  or flooring credit.
